<div class="com-share" data-id="22270" data-title="《刘诗诗和霍建华演的偶像剧，玛丽苏和医术还挺配》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/22270/medium/22270.jpg?1455525982" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/22270.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
